pageContext.claim: “Since my election as President the Dow Jones is up 43% and the NASDAQ Composite almost 50%. Great news for your 401(k)s as they continue to grow. We are bringing back America faster than anyone thought possible!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump regularly takes credit for progress during the last few months of Obama's term. Since he took office, the Dow Jones has increased by around 30 percent. Similarly the NASDAQ Composite has grown around 35 percent.
